>Apache Solr</a> or <a href=\"http://drupal.org/project/sphinx\">Sphinx</a>. These and other <a href=\"@contrib-search\">search-related contributed modules</a> can be downloaded by visiting Drupal.org.','','none'),(4905,'','default','<ul>\n<li>Check if your spelling is correct.</li>\n<li>Remove quotes around phrases to search for each word individually. <em>bike shed</em> will often show more results than <em>&quot;bike shed&quot;</em>.</li>\n<li>Consider loosening your query with <em>OR</em>. <em>bike OR shed</em> will often show more results than <em>bike shed</em>.</li>\n</ul>','','none'),(4906,'','default','Administer search','','none'),(4907,'','default','Use search','','none'),(4908,'','default','Use advanced search','','none'),(4909,'','default','Configure relevance settings for search and other indexing options.','','none'),(4910,'','default','Choose a set of shortcuts to use','','none'),(4911,'','default','Choose a set of shortcuts for this user','','none'),(4912,'','default','You are now using the new %set_name shortcut set. You can edit it from this page or <a href=\"@switch-url\">switch back to a different one.</a>','','none'),(4913,'','default','%user is now using a new shortcut set called %set_name. You can edit it from this page.','','none'),(4914,'','default','You are now using the %set_name shortcut set.','','none'),(4915,'','default','%user is now using the %set_name shortcut set.','','none'),(4916,'','default','Change set','','none'),(4917,'','default','The shortcut set has been updated.','','none'),(4918,'','default','Add new shortcut','','none'),(4919,'','default','Editing @shortcut','','none'),(4920,'','default','The name of the shortcut.','','none'),(4921,'','default','The path to the shortcut.','','none'),(4922,'','default','The link must correspond to a valid path on the site.','','none'),(4923,'','default','The shortcut %link has been updated.','','none'),(4924,'','default','Added a shortcut for %title.','','none'),(4925,'','default','Are y